      • performFinish

        public void performFinish()
        Description copied from interface: IYRCSharedTaskHandler
        This method is called to finish the shared task. The imlementor should finish the task and return a proper response indicating the task status. If the task has a callback handler, then it should be invoked accordingly on task completion or when the task status changes.

        performFinish in interface IYRCSharedTaskHandler
